//output:index.html
html
    head
        title Timestamp Microservice

    body(style="font-size: 90%")
        h2 CharmedSatyr's Timestamp Microservice
        p Type a Unix timestamp or natural language date at the end of this website's URL!
        p This application will use Node.js, Express.js, and other libraries to return a JSON object in response to your entry.
        p The object will include both the Unix timestamp and expanded natural language format for your entry. (Unparsable entries will return&#32;
            span
                code null&#32;
                span values.)
        br
        h3 For example:
        p The entries
        code https://charmedsatyr.herokuapp.com/December%2015,%202015
        br
        code https://charmedsatyr.herokuapp.com/1450105200
        p and
        code https://charmedsatyr.herokuapp.com/15 dec 2015
        p all return
        code {"unix":"1450105200","natural":"Tuesday, December 15th, 2015, 12:00:00 am"}
        br
        p Try it out!
        br
        h6 You can also view this project's source files on&#32;
            a(href='https://github.com/charmedsatyr/timestamp_microservice.git' target='_blank') GitHub.
